{"title":"森林之火","authors":["颜廷奎"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":7,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"森林之火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颜廷奎\t    一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浓烟涂一枚惊叹号"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在祖国北方悬挂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未曾被冰刀霜剑寒风淫雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"征服的强悍，经不住烟蒂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫不经心的袭击"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风，竟助纣为虐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将母亲的一绺秀发掠去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"痛煞几千万儿女的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"森林走了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下几千万公顷空白"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"供我们思索\t　二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大兴安岭高筑烽火台"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼唤绿色兄弟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一片大森林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奇迹般从天而降"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在倾听毕毕剥剥的控诉之后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即以铁腕扼住火魔的喉咙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到它变成一具僵尸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南疆，北疆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"法卡山与大兴安岭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同时为战士耸起丰碑"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}